data.title: Precursors to BEAD Implementation: A Deep Dive Into Prior Broadband Programs
data.meta_description: How will prior broadband programs impact BEAD Implementation?
data.text: The process of rolling out broadband funds under the country’s bipartisan infrastructure law has begun in earnest, with the White House announcement in June of allocations for each state under the Broadband Equity, Access and Deployment program.
